{"tid":283552,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人成日當男朋友係小朋友","createTime":"2017-06-14T08:58:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-14T11:07:14.000Z","uid":13286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d46bd76f6963a11d3af5b6b677c024369f5c46e1","tid":283552,"uid":13286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T08:58:51.000Z","msg":"雖然男朋友外表好man<br />\n但係我面前成個小朋友咁<br />\n又成日挨住我嗲我咁<br />\n佢成日話唔怕黑唔驚鬼<br />\n但我覺得佢其實都係驚<br />\n只係係人地面前扮到唔驚咁<br />\n所以我潛意識就成日覺得<br />\n要保護佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想留低佢係d我覺得危險既地方<br />\n好驚佢有危險<br />\n仲有時諗諗下有少少眼濕濕<br />\n佢話佢係其他人面前唔會咁<br />\n好man同埋唔係我諗得咁離譜<br />\n其實我係極極極細膽女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都覺得自己諗得over左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab7b960342d7f49420ec2de0b11292f8b9c466dd","tid":283552,"uid":121771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T09:00:44.000Z","msg":"扮貞子嚇佢， 驚嘅就飛咗佢"},{"pid":"6107fa56ea05487163b1fdd38cc2cc51f85d2fe4","tid":283552,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T09:01:02.000Z","msg":"湊仔咩"},{"pid":"bb0552dfb52b921e84f640a28b777612dc25abfb","tid":283552,"uid":6267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T09:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你男友好有眼燒，我好想搵呢類女仔做女朋友"},{"pid":"61627a31fede35311d828af155c3e27d41fb7ef3","tid":283552,"uid":6267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T09:01:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你男友好有眼光，我好想搵呢類女仔做女朋友</blockquote